oalscorer: [[2016\u201317 Coppa Italia|2016\u201317]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldfootball.net/goalgetter/ita-coppa-italia-2016-2017/ |title=Coppa Italia 2016/2017 \u2013 Top Scorer |publisher=WorldFootball |access-date=16 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/italcuptops.html |title=Italy - Coppa Italia Top Scorers |publisher=RSSSF |author1=Roberto Di Maggio |author2=Davide Rota |date=4 June 2015 |accessdate=15 June 2015 }}</ref>\n* [[FIFPro World XI|FIFA FIFPro World XI]] 2nd team: 2017<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fifpro.org/news/2016-2017-world-11-the-reserve-teams/en/ |title=2016-2017 World 11: the Reserve Teams - FIFPro World Players' Union |publisher=FIFPro.org |date=23 October 2017 |access-date=23 October 2017}}</ref>\n* FIFA FIFPro World XI 4th team: 2018<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fifpro.org/news/world-11-the-reserve-teams-for-2017-18/en/|title=World 11: The Reserve Team for 2017-18|publisher=FIFPro.org|date=24 September 2018|accessdate=25 September 2018}}</ref>\n* FIFA FIFPro World XI 5th team: 2016<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fifpro.org/news/2016-world-11-the-reserve-teams/en/ |title=2016 World 11: the reserve teams - FIFPro World Players' Union |publisher=FIFPro.org |date=9 January 2017 |access-date=1 October 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Ballon d'Or]]: [[2017 Ballon d'Or|2017]] (15th place)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.francefootball.fr/news/Le-classement-complet-du-ballon-d-or-2017/857283|title=Le classement complet du Ballon d'Or 2017|publisher=France Football|language=French|date=7 December 2017|accessdate=20 December 2017}}</ref>\n\n===Records===\n* [[Supercoppa Italiana#All-time top goalscorers|Supercoppa Italiana all-time top scorer]]: 4 goals<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldfootball.net/alltime_goalgetter/ita-supercoppa/tore/1/|title=All-time top goalscorers|publisher=worldfootball.net}}</ref><ref name=myjuve.it>{{cite web|url=http://www.myjuve.it/statistiche-giocatori-juventus/classifica-reti_segnate-